{"arkId":"cl010098689","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010098689","modified ":"2025-12-21","title":"Monstrance reliquaire","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Monstrance reliquaire"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : gothique (Occident-\u003Emoyen \u00e2ge)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1350 - 1415","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 503 - Jeanne d\u0027Evreux, Vitrine 27","room":"Salle 503, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1350,"endYear":1415,"imprecision":"","text":"XIVe-XVe si\u00e8cle (?)","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Anonyme","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q4233718"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 5565","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; monstrance-reliquaire = monstrance reliquaire","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le pied, de forme barlongue, est taill\u00e9 \u00e0 huit lobes d\u00e9crits alternativement suivant des demi-cercles, ou suivant des courbes et des contre-courbes. Au centre de ce pied se dresse une tige \u00e0 six pans, garnie \u00e0 sa base de contreforts encadrant des fenestrages de style gothique garnis de plaques recouvertes d\u0027\u00e9maux translucides. A mi-hauteur de la tige, d\u0027une corbeille affectant la forme d\u0027une enceinte foritifi\u00e9e, sortent des volutes termin\u00e9es par des chapiteaux supportant deux grandes figures d\u0027anges, les ailes \u00e9ploy\u00e9es, portant les flambeaux. Ces statuettes flanquent le reliquaire lui-m\u00eame, compos\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9difice gothique plus long que large, orn\u00e9 sur ses six faces de six gables pointus abritant des fenestrages gothiques, au fond desquelles sont fix\u00e9es des plaques d\u0027argent recouvertes d\u0027\u00e9maux translucides. Des contreforts s\u00e9parent chacun de ces gables et font une forte saillie sur l\u0027architecture. Trois fl\u00e8ches, l\u0027une m\u00e9diane, \u00e9tablie sur plan rectangulaire, deux lat\u00e9rales, sur plan triangulaire, orn\u00e9e chacune de fenestrages gothiques surmont\u00e9s de gables accompagn\u00e9s de clochetons et de gargouilles, forment le couronnent de l\u0027\u00e9difice. Le clocher central se termine par un fleuron \u00e0 deux \u00e9tages largement \u00e9panoui.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; + BA\/RCK (sur le pied)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"80,5","displayDimension":"80,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nTechnique : dor\u00e9 = dorure (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9mail de basse taille sur argent (techniques m\u00e9tal-\u003E\u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux-\u003E\u00e9mail de basse taille)","placeOfCreation":"Barcelone (Espagne-\u003ECatalogne)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection du baron Adolphe de Rothschild (1823-1900) ; Legs Adolphe de Rothschild, 1901.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Rothschild, Adolphe de","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"},{"value":"Baronne Rothschild, Julie de","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1901","startYear":1901,"endYear":1901}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"period":[{"value":"gothique"}],"place":[{"value":"Barcelone"}],"objectType":[{"value":"monstrance-reliquaire = monstrance reliquaire"},{"value":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Marquet de Vasselot, Jean-Joseph, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre. Catalogue sommaire de l\u0027orf\u00e8vrerie, de l\u0027\u00e9maillerie et des gemmes du Moyen Age au XVII\u00e8me si\u00e8cle, Paris, Gaston Braun \u00e9diteur, 1914","bibliographyDate":"1914","bibliographyDetail":"MV 99","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Molinier, Emile, Donation de M. le baron Adolphe de Rothschild (Mus\u00e9e national du Louvre), Paris, E. L\u00e9vy, 1902","bibliographyDate":"1902","bibliographyDetail":"p. 9, n\u00b0 15","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Migeon, Gaston, \u00ab Les accroissements des mus\u00e9es. Le Legs Adolphe de Rothschild au Louvre \u00bb, Les Arts, 2, mars 1902, p. 8-14","bibliographyDate":"","bibliographyDetail":"p. 13, fig. p. 11","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[{"value":"Galerie du temps 2018-2019, Louvre-Lens, 15\/09\/2018 - 04\/12\/2019 "}],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000098689\/0000242676_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000098689\/0000242676_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2008 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000098689\/0000242513_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000098689\/0000242513_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2008 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gilles Berizzi","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000098689\/0000242514_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/c